    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler dev-utils SIG 是什么？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "openEuler dev-utils SIG（Special Interest Group，特别兴趣小组）负责 The dev-utils team is responsible for maintain the SDK and libraries which help developers for OpenEuler.。该 SIG 共有 49 名核心成员，维护 301 个代码仓库，属于 基础设施与工具 领域。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "如何参与 openEuler dev-utils SIG？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "参与 openEuler dev-utils SIG 的方式：1）向相关仓库（如 src-openeuler/btop、openeuler/c2rust、src-openeuler/c2rust）提交 Pull Request；2）订阅邮件列表 dev@openeuler.org；3）参加 SIG 定期工作会议，会议信息见 openEuler 官网活动日历。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler dev-utils SIG 包含哪些代码仓库？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "openEuler dev-utils SIG 共维护 301 个代码仓库，主要包括：src-openeuler/btop、openeuler/c2rust、src-openeuler/c2rust 等。完整列表见 https://www.openeuler.org/zh/sig/dev-utils。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler dev-utils SIG 的 Maintainer 是谁？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
